Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:12.32,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:14.66,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:51.39,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:55.74,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it... that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:02.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna! Don't rush off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:04.25,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:13.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:16.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:17.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:41.70,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mysterious sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:46.58,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Like grains of sand \Nscraping against each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:51.12,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Like Manaka-san's heart pounding...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:52.91,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Like it was hitting waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:11.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shioshishio...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.00,Episode-Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Eighteen: \NShioshishio
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.86,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:02.16,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Everyone's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:03.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.36,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If everyone was wandering \Naround like sleepwalkers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:07.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.26,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,This is Shioshishio...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:20.36,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Where Hikari, Kaname-san, Chisaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.39,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,and Manaka-san lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.59,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.11,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:38.39,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.33,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,The light is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:43.17,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently with this, \Nthey can find out all sorts of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.68,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,like the salt density and \Nthe flow of the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.97,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.06,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.52,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look for Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Old man Hayakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.98,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he was trying \Nto guard the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:25.68,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we were told \Nthat during the hibernation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.29,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,we should be relaxing at our own houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.56,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,His back's gonna hurt when he wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.36,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He's just sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:34.31,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.21,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's just sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:40.12,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Once he wakes up, \Nhe'll be back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:43.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.58,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,This was the place I \Nalways dreamed of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.59,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:10.72,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:11.68,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.13,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, they're just hibernating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's rude to everyone if you \Nkeep looking so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.14,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:21.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that all of \Nthem are dead or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.52,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.55,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:33.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I go home for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:34.71,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:39.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go calm down \Nbefore we look for Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:44.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be too worked up and I have \Na feeling I'll embarrass myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:48.22,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,That's possible. I don't have \Nany faith that I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:52.49,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back as soon as possible, \Nso could you wait here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.68,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.81,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:09.07,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time being \Nin Shioshishio, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.62,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,For Hikari and Kaname,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:16.08,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,this is probably a Shioshishio \Nthey don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:35.31,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't mean anything by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.97,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:41.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they really are \Njust sleeping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:42.81,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.50,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's just hibernation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:49.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama and the adults \Nweren't lying, were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.57,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, why'd we wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:54.42,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.29,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:06.13,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna's birth mother was \Nfrom the sea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:11.24,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted her to think it was pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.51,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna's mom's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.81,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Our Shioshishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.46,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.28,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The world I always imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:21.79,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The world I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:26.84,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,With roads I didn't know, \Nand people I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:28.21,book,book,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}Yesterday was a storm, today is a lull.\NWhat will the sea be like tomorrow?\NWhat do the two sea slugs wonder?\N"The light wavers, pepepu."\N"The wave draws nearer, pepupu."\N"The wavering light is like a net."\N"The drawing wave is the song of the sea."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:32.41,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Because the world I had \Nimagined was so bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.30,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Because it was shining...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:38.29,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know... what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:44.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Old man Hayakawa was \Nacting like a guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.66,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He was always serious \Nabout wanting to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:48.56,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but something was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:53.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, did you know you have a grandkid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:56.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Not just Miuna, but a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.66,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.89,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He's almost four now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:04.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, I just found \Nout the other day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:15.05,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:30.41,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.17,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what Akira's \Nspecial move is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:42.10,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's kancho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.54,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do about that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like he's \Nnot cute or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:49.19,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, he is cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:52.42,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari says he looks like \Nme when I was younger,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.63,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:11:00.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to meet him and get\N your opinion... or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:07.43,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.23,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:16.69,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I just say Manaka-san's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:20.85,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:27.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and the reason we were\Nable to come here is Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:30.39,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She's able to be in the sea now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's surprising, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:35.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And then she heard some weird sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:37.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and it led us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:40.70,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,the real Shioshishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:46.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we were able to come \Nback here thanks to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:50.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I didn't say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:53.10,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"Thanks for bringing us here."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:56.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell Miuna that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:15.55,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The Shioshishio that \NI always dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.59,2nd Year,sign,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Year
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:20.09,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But the way I acted...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:23.59,Entrance Ceremony,sign in picture,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:23.59,New Students,sign by hand,0000,0000,0000,,New Students
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:23.59,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up hurting Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:34.35,You haven't grown much,sign,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't grown much, Manaka.\NNeither have you, Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:52.93,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.13,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:05.35,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The place I thought of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:08.55,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,dreamed of... inside the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:31.45,I'm here,blue,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:31.45,160 Chisaki,sign,0000,0000,0000,,160 Chisaki\N157 Hikari\N155 Kaname\N154 Chisaki\N152 Manaka\N149 Manaka
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.42,Music Room,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Music Room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.51,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:54.35,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.74,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I told her not to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:58.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Did you actually look?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.06,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to argue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:02.36,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.59,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.09,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:07.49,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Those weren't there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.10,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:26.94,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:28.34,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:30.05,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:33.72,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a scale, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.27,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,"Scale"? You mean like a fish's?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:39.19,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Right. That scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.67,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Was the school inside the sea fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.19,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Then that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:48.70,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Shioshishio a wonderful place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.15,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:53.78,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.20,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,"Looking for"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.91,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:02.21,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not come here in search of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.95,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.80,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.67,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:13.22,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You're a god... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.59,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I am nothing more than a scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:17.28,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:18.06,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:23.53,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me where Manaka-san is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:26.44,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.87,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you were \Ntruly looking for,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:32.03,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.48,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:36.45,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The thing I'm looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.48,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,is Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:39.46,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.46,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:45.32,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,What an audacious child you are, \Nlying to the face of a servant of a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:46.55,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.25,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.01,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.97,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.54,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:59.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We told you to stay right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:03.71,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:04.61,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.64,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:08.43,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:10.32,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:14.21,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I think I just met god.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:15.70,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"God"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Sea God?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:20.99,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's talking about Uroko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.58,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.33,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he didn't fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:28.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He's the protector of this village, \Nso he probably wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.17,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.65,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:50.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This was a play area \Nfor us and we used to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:52.51,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,run around here when we \Nwere in grade school,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.20,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never seen this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.83,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Are these...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.64,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,All Ojoshi-samas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:22.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,These are probably the Ojoshi-samas that \Nwere sent down over the years...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:23.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:27.15,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,A graveyard of Ojoshi-samas...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.53,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.81,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikari! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:39.09,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan, wait right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:45.37,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:50.51,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:51.78,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:12.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.82,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.17,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu told us, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:29.50,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,We can't force people who\Nare sleeping to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:33.19,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows what kind of \Neffect that may have on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.47,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:45.23,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you were looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:51.02,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,"I just wanted to come to Shioshishio."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:55.07,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,That is nothing more than a child's fib.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:19:00.65,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:07.28,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Once something appears, \Nsomething is lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:11.59,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, it all equals out in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:17.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka, what are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:20.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All of us are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:23.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're not an Ojoshi-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:26.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,so you don't have to be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:33.82,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san's trying to wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:38.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Ena?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:53.59,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,This sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.42,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.29,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Her Ena's coming off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:00.70,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,She's losing her Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:03.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:05.39,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why is something like this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.73,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:10.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, Manaka's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:21.57,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.51,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:24.12,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to take Manaka to the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.53,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Manaka's going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.43,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:30.75,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.42,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Turn away for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.37,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.27,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:21:01.00,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the Sea God is angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.29,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,About us taking Manaka back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.66,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The hell if I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.54,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Miuna-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:34.16,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari! Not that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:36.40,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The sound is coming from over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:42.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:31.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:35.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far I reached, \Nit didn't get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:37.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:39.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never letting go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:40.14,Episode-Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Nineteen: \NThe Lost, Lost Little...
